wdi-FM.AST.PRVT.ZG.M3.def: Claims on private sector (IFS line 32D..ZK or 32D..ZF) include gross credit from the financial system to individuals, enterprises, nonfinancial public entities not included under net domestic credit, and financial institutions not included elsewhere.
wdi-FM.AST.PRVT.ZG.M3.name: Claims on private sector
wdi-FM.AST.PRVT.ZG.M3.source: International Monetary Fund, International Financial Statistics and data files.
